      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "Since then, we have routinely performed thrombophilia screening tests in addition to conventional coagulation test for evaluation of donors and established these screening criteria for donor selection and venous thromboembolic events (VTE) prophylaxis [CITATION_1] ."
